---

### Page-Level Navigation

#### Jobs Feed Page

```
Tabs (horizontal):
[New] [Qualified] [Skip] [All]

Filters (top right):
- Search box
- Date posted
- Location
- Industry
- Favorites toggle

Sort (dropdown):
- Most recent
- Relevance
- Company size

View toggle:
[Grid View] [List View]
```

#### Companies Page

```
View modes (top):
[List View] [Kanban Board] [Table View]

Filters:
- Status/Stage (dropdown)
- Owner (multi-select)
- Industry
- Date added
- Favorites toggle
- Search

Sort:
- Last activity
- Name A-Z
- Date added
- Status
```

#### People Page

```
Filters:
- Outreach status
- Company (dropdown)
- Role/Title
- Owner
- Date added
- Favorites toggle
- Search by name/email

Sort:
- Last contacted
- Name A-Z
- Company
- Response likelihood (future: AI score)
```

#### Conversations Page

```
Layout: Inbox-style (Gmail-like)

Left panel (30%):
- Thread list
- Filters:
  - Unread
  - Needs reply
  - Starred
  - Archived
- Search threads

Right panel (70%):
- Thread viewer
- Reply box
- Quick actions:
  - Mark as done
  - Set reminder
  - Move company stage
```

